flowchart TD

    IMG([Input Image]):::input
    TILES([Tile Dataset]):::input

    HOU[Houdini SOP Authoring\nPoint Grid · Attributes · Chunk Assignment]:::houdini

    PART[Chunk Partitioning\n.bgeo.sc per chunk]:::pdg
    WORK[PDG Work Items\nOne per chunk · Stateless · Retry-safe]:::pdg

    GPU[GPU Dispatch\nOne thread per cell]:::nvidia
    MATCH[CIE76 Delta-E Tile Matching\nBrute-force · LAB space]:::kernel
    IDS[(tile_id Array\n.npy sidecar per chunk)]:::kernel

    INST[Instance Assembly\nPositions · Orientations · Scales]:::usd
    CHUNK[USD Chunk Export\nUsdGeomPointInstancer per chunk]:::usd
    AGG[USD Layer Aggregation\nmosaic_root.usda · sublayer composition]:::usd

    UE[Unreal Engine 5\nStage Actor · HISM Pipeline · Materials]:::unreal
    OUT([Render Output]):::output

    IMG --> HOU
    TILES --> HOU
    HOU --> PART
    PART --> WORK
    WORK --> GPU
    GPU --> MATCH
    MATCH --> IDS
    IDS --> INST
    INST --> CHUNK
    CHUNK --> AGG
    AGG --> UE
    UE --> OUT

